snippet.title: Stickman Ice Hockey (Official Trailer)
snippet.description:
Djinnworks is very proud to announce the first Trailer of Stickman Ice Hockey, coming very soon for iOS and Android. Stickman Ice Hockey has the perfect balance between pure Arcade fun and awesome Ice Hockey Simulation, perfectly implemented for mobile game experiences. Stickman Ice Hockey joins our Stickman Sports game collection consisting of Stickman Soccer, Stickman Basketball and Stickman Tennis. 

Available soon for iOS, Android and Amazon.

We would love to read your impressions!
